Ingredients:
59% concentrated vegetable bouillon (water, carrots, leek, red bell pepper, CELERIAC) salt, vegetable fats (palm), sugar, yeast extract, parsley, gelling agents (xanthan gum (E 415) , locust bean gum (E 410) ), fenugreek extract, spices (CELERY seeds, lovage root, nutmeg, pepper), caramel syrup, maltodextrin.
